### CMS publish item
POST {{host}}/cms/events
Authorization: {{cmsAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "type": "publish",
    "id": "walkthrough-item-1",
    "payload": {
      "title": "Hello world",
      "slug": "hello-world",
      "body": "First published version"
    },
    "version": 1,
    "timestamp": "2026-04-06T12:00:00Z"
  }
]

### CMS publish update
POST {{host}}/cms/events
Authorization: {{cmsAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "type": "publish",
    "id": "walkthrough-item-1",
    "payload": {
      "title": "Hello world updated",
      "slug": "hello-world",
      "body": "Second published version"
    },
    "version": 2,
    "timestamp": "2026-04-06T12:05:00Z"
  }
]

### CMS unpublish item
POST {{host}}/cms/events
Authorization: {{cmsAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "type": "unpublish",
    "id": "walkthrough-item-2",
    "payload": {
      "title": "Unpublished item",
      "slug": "unpublished-item",
      "body": "This should only be visible to admins"
    },
    "version": 1,
    "timestamp": "2026-04-06T12:10:00Z"
  }
]

### CMS stale publish event
POST {{host}}/cms/events
Authorization: {{cmsAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "type": "publish",
    "id": "walkthrough-item-1",
    "payload": {
      "title": "Old content",
      "slug": "hello-world",
      "body": "This should be ignored"
    },
    "version": 1,
    "timestamp": "2026-04-06T11:00:00Z"
  }
]

### CMS validation failure example
POST {{host}}/cms/events
Authorization: {{cmsAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "type": "publish",
    "id": "walkthrough-item-invalid",
    "payload": {
      "title": "Missing version"
    },
    "timestamp": "2026-04-06T12:25:00Z"
  }
]

### Consumer get all visible content
GET {{host}}/api/content-items
Authorization: {{consumerAuth}}
Accept: application/json

### Consumer get visible item by id
GET {{host}}/api/content-items/walkthrough-item-1
Authorization: {{consumerAuth}}
Accept: application/json

### Consumer get unpublished item by id - expected 404
GET {{host}}/api/content-items/walkthrough-item-2
Authorization: {{consumerAuth}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin get all content including unpublished/admin-disabled
GET {{host}}/api/content-items
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin get unpublished item by id
GET {{host}}/api/content-items/walkthrough-item-2
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin disable published item
POST {{host}}/api/content-items/walkthrough-item-1/disable
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### Consumer get disabled item by id - expected 404
GET {{host}}/api/content-items/walkthrough-item-1
Authorization: {{consumerAuth}}
Accept: application/json

### Admin enable previously disabled item
POST {{host}}/api/content-items/walkthrough-item-1/enable
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### Consumer can see re-enabled item again
GET {{host}}/api/content-items/walkthrough-item-1
Authorization: {{consumerAuth}}
Accept: application/json

### CMS hard delete
POST {{host}}/cms/events
Authorization: {{cmsAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "type": "delete",
    "id": "walkthrough-item-1",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-06T12:30:00Z"
  }
]

### Consumer get deleted item by id - expected 404
GET {{host}}/api/content-items/walkthrough-item-1
Authorization: {{consumerAuth}}
Accept: application/json
